<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SL Alianças | Alianças de Moeda Antiga Premium</title>
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>

    <style>
        /* --- VARIÁVEIS DE DESIGN --- */
        :root {
            --bg-principal: #0b0b0c;
            --bg-card: rgba(20, 20, 22, 0.7);
            --borda-glass: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
            --cor-ouro: #d4af37;
            --cor-ouro-hover: #f3cb46;
            --texto-claro: #f3f4f6;
            --texto-mutado: #9ca3af;
            --font-stack: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            --transicao: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        /* --- RESET & BASE --- */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-stack);
            background-color: var(--bg-principal);
            color: var(--texto-claro);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            /* Detalhe de iluminação de fundo (Glow tecnológico) */
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08) 0%, transparent 40%);
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            transition: var(--transicao);
        }

        /* --- HEADER & NAV --- */
        .header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            background-color: rgba(11, 11, 12, 0.8);
        }

        .nav-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .header__logo h1 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, var(--cor-ouro) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .nav__list {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            list-style: none;
        }

        .nav__link {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--texto-mutated);
            position: relative;
            padding: 0.5rem 0;
        }

        .nav__link:hover, .nav__link.active {
            color: var(--cor-ouro);
        }

        .nav__link::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background-color: var(--cor-ouro);
            transition: var(--transicao);
        }

        .nav__link:hover::after, .nav__link.active::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* --- HERO / MAIN CONTENT --- */
        .main-content {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem 2rem;
        }

        /* Efeito Glassmorphism no Card */
        .hero-card {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid var(--borda-glass);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 3.5rem;
            max-width: 650px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), 
                        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            animation: fadeln 1s ease-out;
        }

        .hero-card h2 {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .hero-card p {
            color: var(--texto-mutated);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* Botão Moderno */
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            background-color: var(--cor-ouro);
            color: #000;
            padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--cor-ouro-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
        }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--texto-mutated);
            background-color: #080809;
        }

        /* --- FLOATING WHATSAPP --- */
        .whatsapp-float {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 2rem;
            right: 2rem;
            background-color: #25d366;
            color: white;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.3);
            z-index: 999;
        }

        .whatsapp-float:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1) translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.5);
        }

        /* --- ANIMATION --- */
        @keyframes fadeln {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* --- RESPONSIVIDADE --- */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-container {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.25rem;
            }
            .nav__list {
                gap: 1.25rem;
            }
            .hero-card {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }
            .hero-card h2 {
                font-size: 1.75rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="header">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <div class="header__logo">
                <h1>SL ALIANÇAS</h1>
            </div>
            <nav class="nav">
                <ul class="nav__list">
                    <li><a href="index.html" class="nav__link active">Início</a></li>
                    <li><a href="galeria.html" class="nav__link">Galeria</a></li>
                    <li><a href="como-chegar.html" class="nav__link">Como Chegar</a></li>
                    <li><a href="contato.html" class="nav__link">Contato</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main-content">
        <section class="hero-card">
            <h2>Eternizando Momentos com Brilho & Alta Qualidade</h2>
            <p>Seja bem-vindo à SL Alianças. Somos especialistas na fabricação artesanal de alianças de moeda antiga. Nossas peças possuem a cor e o brilho do ouro 18k, não descascam e têm durabilidade eterna.</p>
            <p>Trabalhamos com modelos anatômicos personalizáveis, pensados para o seu total conforto e estilo.</p>
            <a href="galeria.html" class="btn-primary">
                Ver Modelos 
                <i data-lucide="arrow-right" style="width: 18px; height: 18px;"></i>
            </a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <a href="https://wa.me/SEUNUMERO" class="whatsapp-float" target="_blank" aria-label="Contato via WhatsApp">
        <i data-lucide="message-circle" style="width: 28px; height: 28px; fill: currentColor;"></i>
    </a>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2026 SL Alianças — Joias com Durabilidade Eterna. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>